The '''Emperor's Voice''' was an exalted level of [[Dark side adept/Legends|Dark Side Adept]] loyal to [[Emperor/Legends|Emperor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] at the time of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]].

==History==
It served as a parallel to the [[Emperor's Hand/Legends|Emperor's Hands]], [[Emperor's Eye]]s, and [[Emperor's Reach]].
[[Maarek Stele/Legends|Maarek Stele]] was an Emperor's Voice as well as a Reach and a Hand.

